# HTML Related Instructions

- keep using the templating language Jinja2Templates
- don't change the [_base.html](mdc:workflows/crewai_flow/templates/_base.html)
- only expand the [form.html](mdc:workflows/crewai_flow/templates/form.html) to capture all required input paramters for the CrewAI flow
- make choosing the output format (markdown or json) always a dropdown menu in the form
